{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1960,"text":"The human voice:"},{"time":4070,"text":"It's the instrument we all play."},{"time":6610,"text":"It's the most powerful sound\nin the world, probably."},{"time":9093,"text":"It's the only one that can start a war\nor say \"I love you.\""},{"time":11940,"text":"And yet many people have the experience"},{"time":13822,"text":"that when they speak, people\ndon't listen to them."},{"time":16210,"text":"And why is that?"},{"time":17346,"text":"How can we speak powerfully\nto make change in the world?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":21485,"text":"What I'd like to suggest,"},{"time":22821,"text":"there are a number of habits\nthat we need to move away from."},{"time":25690,"text":"I've assembled for your pleasure here\nseven deadly sins of speaking."},{"time":29444,"text":"I'm not pretending\nthis is an exhaustive list,"},{"time":31876,"text":"but these seven, I think, are pretty large\nhabits that we can all fall into."}]},{"cues":[{"time":37132,"text":"First, gossip."},{"time":39989,"text":"Speaking ill of somebody\nwho's not present."},{"time":42700,"text":"Not a nice habit,\nand we know perfectly well"},{"time":44820,"text":"the person gossiping, five minutes later,\nwill be gossiping about us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":49771,"text":"Second, judging."},{"time":51515,"text":"We know people who are like this\nin conversation,"},{"time":53923,"text":"and it's very hard to listen to somebody"},{"time":55879,"text":"if you know that you're being judged\nand found wanting at the same time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":60029,"text":"Third, negativity."},{"time":62447,"text":"You can fall into this."},{"time":63759,"text":"My mother, in the last years of her life,\nbecame very negative,"},{"time":66820,"text":"and it's hard to listen."},{"time":68166,"text":"I remember one day, I said to her,\n\"It's October 1 today,\""},{"time":70923,"text":"and she said, \"I know, isn't it dreadful?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":73040,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":75262,"text":"It's hard to listen\nwhen somebody's that negative."}]},{"cues":[{"time":77635,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":78931,"text":"And another form\nof negativity, complaining."},{"time":81475,"text":"Well, this is the national art of the U.K."},{"time":85542,"text":"It's our national sport."},{"time":86977,"text":"We complain about the weather, sport,\nabout politics, about everything,"},{"time":90435,"text":"but actually, complaining is viral misery."},{"time":92555,"text":"It's not spreading sunshine\nand lightness in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":96292,"text":"Excuses."}]},{"cues":[{"time":98048,"text":"We've all met this guy."},{"time":99396,"text":"Maybe we've all been this guy."},{"time":100996,"text":"Some people have a blamethrower."},{"time":103490,"text":"They just pass it on to everybody else"},{"time":105718,"text":"and don't take responsibility\nfor their actions,"},{"time":108046,"text":"and again, hard to listen\nto somebody who is being like that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110982,"text":"Penultimate, the sixth of the seven,"},{"time":112804,"text":"embroidery, exaggeration."},{"time":116210,"text":"It demeans our language,\nactually, sometimes."},{"time":118638,"text":"For example, if I see something\nthat really is awesome,"},{"time":121930,"text":"what do I call it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":123220,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":125840,"text":"And then, of course,\nthis exaggeration becomes lying,"},{"time":129300,"text":"and we don't want to listen\nto people we know are lying to us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":132323,"text":"And finally, dogmatism."},{"time":135688,"text":"The confusion of facts with opinions."},{"time":139323,"text":"When those two things get conflated,"},{"time":141262,"text":"you're listening into the wind."},{"time":142763,"text":"You know, somebody is bombarding you\nwith their opinions as if they were true."},{"time":146454,"text":"It's difficult to listen to that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":148547,"text":"So here they are, seven deadly\nsins of speaking."},{"time":151588,"text":"These are things I think we need to avoid."},{"time":154021,"text":"But is there a positive\nway to think about this?"},{"time":156890,"text":"Yes, there is."},{"time":158458,"text":"I'd like to suggest that there are four\nreally powerful cornerstones, foundations,"},{"time":163974,"text":"that we can stand on if we want our speech"},{"time":166420,"text":"to be powerful and to make\nchange in the world."},{"time":170288,"text":"Fortunately, these things spell a word."},{"time":172523,"text":"The word is \"hail,\" and it has\na great definition as well."},{"time":175619,"text":"I'm not talking about the stuff\nthat falls from the sky"},{"time":178287,"text":"and hits you on the head."},{"time":179575,"text":"I'm talking about this definition,"},{"time":181219,"text":"to greet or acclaim enthusiastically,"},{"time":183040,"text":"which is how I think\nour words will be received"},{"time":185307,"text":"if we stand on these four things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186903,"text":"So what do they stand for?"},{"time":188425,"text":"See if you can guess."},{"time":190320,"text":"The H, honesty, of course,"},{"time":193283,"text":"being true in what you say,\nbeing straight and clear."},{"time":196254,"text":"The A is authenticity,\njust being yourself."},{"time":200295,"text":"A friend of mine described it as\nstanding in your own truth,"},{"time":203505,"text":"which I think is a lovely way to put it."},{"time":205443,"text":"The I is integrity, being your word,"},{"time":208079,"text":"actually doing what you say,"},{"time":209867,"text":"and being somebody people can trust."},{"time":212358,"text":"And the L is love."},{"time":215130,"text":"I don't mean romantic love,"},{"time":217251,"text":"but I do mean wishing people\nwell, for two reasons."},{"time":220660,"text":"First of all, I think absolute honesty\nmay not be what we want."},{"time":224074,"text":"I mean, my goodness,\nyou look ugly this morning."},{"time":226663,"text":"Perhaps that's not necessary."},{"time":230021,"text":"Tempered with love, of course,\nhonesty is a great thing."},{"time":233379,"text":"But also, if you're really\nwishing somebody well,"},{"time":236474,"text":"it's very hard to judge\nthem at the same time."},{"time":239111,"text":"I'm not even sure you can do\nthose two things simultaneously."},{"time":243310,"text":"So hail."}]},{"cues":[{"time":244910,"text":"Also, now that's what you say,"},{"time":246667,"text":"and it's like the old song,\nit is what you say,"},{"time":248935,"text":"it's also the way that you say it."},{"time":250638,"text":"You have an amazing toolbox."},{"time":252410,"text":"This instrument is incredible,"},{"time":254270,"text":"and yet this is a toolbox\nthat very few people have ever opened."},{"time":257810,"text":"I'd like to have a little rummage\nin there with you now"},{"time":260431,"text":"and just pull a few tools out"},{"time":261855,"text":"that you might like to take\naway and play with,"},{"time":264118,"text":"which will increase\nthe power of your speaking."}]},{"cues":[{"time":266442,"text":"Register, for example."},{"time":267986,"text":"Now, falsetto register may not\nbe very useful most of the time,"},{"time":272180,"text":"but there's a register in between."},{"time":274234,"text":"I'm not going to get very\ntechnical about this"},{"time":276419,"text":"for any of you who are voice coaches."},{"time":278205,"text":"You can locate your voice, however."},{"time":279942,"text":"So if I talk up here in my nose,\nyou can hear the difference."},{"time":282824,"text":"If I go down here in my throat,"},{"time":284332,"text":"which is where most of us\nspeak from most of the time."},{"time":286985,"text":"But if you want weight,"},{"time":288642,"text":"you need to go down here to the chest."},{"time":291120,"text":"You hear the difference?"},{"time":292730,"text":"We vote for politicians\nwith lower voices, it's true,"},{"time":296770,"text":"because we associate depth with power"},{"time":299738,"text":"and with authority."},{"time":302445,"text":"That's register."}]},{"cues":[{"time":304134,"text":"Then we have timbre."},{"time":305501,"text":"It's the way your voice feels."},{"time":307270,"text":"Again, the research shows"},{"time":308626,"text":"that we prefer voices\nwhich are rich, smooth, warm,"},{"time":312424,"text":"like hot chocolate."},{"time":314635,"text":"Well if that's not you,\nthat's not the end of the world,"},{"time":317923,"text":"because you can train."},{"time":319365,"text":"Go and get a voice coach."},{"time":320609,"text":"And there are amazing things you can do"},{"time":322491,"text":"with breathing, with posture,\nand with exercises"},{"time":324921,"text":"to improve the timbre of your voice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":327435,"text":"Then prosody. I love prosody."},{"time":329227,"text":"This is the sing-song, the meta-language"},{"time":331403,"text":"that we use in order to impart meaning."},{"time":333477,"text":"It's root one for meaning in conversation."},{"time":336315,"text":"People who speak all on one note\nare really quite hard to listen to"},{"time":340395,"text":"if they don't have any prosody at all."},{"time":342611,"text":"That's where the word\n\"monotonic\" comes from,"},{"time":345586,"text":"or monotonous, monotone."},{"time":348306,"text":"Also, we have repetitive\nprosody now coming in,"},{"time":351603,"text":"where every sentence ends\nas if it were a question"},{"time":354323,"text":"when it's actually not\na question, it's a statement?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":356824,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":359154,"text":"And if you repeat that one,"},{"time":360740,"text":"it's actually restricting your ability\nto communicate through prosody,"},{"time":364108,"text":"which I think is a shame,"},{"time":365994,"text":"so let's try and break that habit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":369315,"text":"Pace."}]},{"cues":[{"time":370418,"text":"I can get very excited by saying\nsomething really quickly,"},{"time":373203,"text":"or I can slow right down to emphasize,"},{"time":376579,"text":"and at the end of that, of course,\nis our old friend silence."},{"time":382555,"text":"There's nothing wrong with a bit\nof silence in a talk, is there?"},{"time":386561,"text":"We don't have to fill it with ums and ahs."},{"time":389833,"text":"It can be very powerful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":391823,"text":"Of course, pitch often\ngoes along with pace"},{"time":394151,"text":"to indicate arousal, but you\ncan do it just with pitch."},{"time":396795,"text":"Where did you leave my keys?"},{"time":398383,"text":"(Higher pitch) Where did you\nleave my keys?"},{"time":400487,"text":"So, slightly different meaning\nin those two deliveries."}]},{"cues":[{"time":404156,"text":"And finally, volume."},{"time":406402,"text":"(Loud) I can get really excited\nby using volume."},{"time":409803,"text":"Sorry about that, if I startled anybody."},{"time":411980,"text":"Or, I can have you really pay attention\nby getting very quiet."},{"time":416707,"text":"Some people broadcast the whole time."},{"time":418527,"text":"Try not to do that."},{"time":419900,"text":"That's called sodcasting,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":421752,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":423445,"text":"Imposing your sound on people around you\ncarelessly and inconsiderately."},{"time":428013,"text":"Not nice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":429115,"text":"Of course, where this all comes\ninto play most of all"},{"time":431671,"text":"is when you've got something\nreally important to do."},{"time":434199,"text":"It might be standing on a stage like this\nand giving a talk to people."},{"time":437651,"text":"It might be proposing marriage,"},{"time":439539,"text":"asking for a raise, a wedding speech."},{"time":442693,"text":"Whatever it is, if it's really important,"},{"time":444699,"text":"you owe it to yourself\nto look at this toolbox"},{"time":448472,"text":"and the engine that it's going to work on,"},{"time":450509,"text":"and no engine works well\nwithout being warmed up."},{"time":453604,"text":"Warm up your voice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":455482,"text":"Actually, let me show you how to do that."},{"time":457557,"text":"Would you all like to stand\nup for a moment?"},{"time":460536,"text":"I'm going to show you"},{"time":461691,"text":"the six vocal warm-up exercises\nthat I do before every talk I ever do."},{"time":466925,"text":"Any time you're going to talk\nto anybody important, do these."},{"time":469859,"text":"First, arms up, deep breath in,"},{"time":472662,"text":"and sigh out, ahhhhh, like that."},{"time":475764,"text":"One more time."},{"time":477392,"text":"Ahhhh, very good."},{"time":480390,"text":"Now we're going to warm up our lips,"},{"time":482132,"text":"and we're going to go Ba, Ba, Ba, Ba,"},{"time":484484,"text":"Ba, Ba, Ba, Ba. Very good."},{"time":487436,"text":"And now, brrrrrrrrrr,"},{"time":490876,"text":"just like when you were a kid."},{"time":492426,"text":"Brrrr. Now your lips\nshould be coming alive."},{"time":494853,"text":"We're going to do the tongue next"},{"time":496528,"text":"with exaggerated la, la, la,\nla, la, la, la, la, la."},{"time":500850,"text":"Beautiful. You're getting\nreally good at this."},{"time":503065,"text":"And then, roll an R. Rrrrrrr."},{"time":505955,"text":"That's like champagne for the tongue."},{"time":508171,"text":"Finally, and if I can only do one,"},{"time":510491,"text":"the pros call this the siren."},{"time":512298,"text":"It's really good. It starts\nwith \"we\" and goes to \"aw.\""},{"time":514942,"text":"The \"we\" is high, the \"aw\" is low."},{"time":516586,"text":"So you go, weeeaawww, weeeaawww."}]},{"cues":[{"time":522706,"text":"Fantastic. Give yourselves\na round of applause."},{"time":524969,"text":"Take a seat, thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":526238,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":527712,"text":"Next time you speak, do those in advance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":530336,"text":"Now let me just put this\nin context to close."},{"time":532976,"text":"This is a serious point here."},{"time":535272,"text":"This is where we are now, right?"},{"time":537103,"text":"We speak not very well"},{"time":538768,"text":"to people who simply aren't listening"},{"time":540636,"text":"in an environment that's all\nabout noise and bad acoustics."},{"time":543555,"text":"I have talked about that on this stage\nin different phases."},{"time":546798,"text":"What would the world be like"},{"time":548432,"text":"if we were speaking powerfully"},{"time":550152,"text":"to people who were listening consciously"},{"time":552208,"text":"in environments which were\nactually fit for purpose?"},{"time":555602,"text":"Or to make that a bit larger,"},{"time":558585,"text":"what would the world be like"},{"time":559943,"text":"if we were creating sound consciously"},{"time":562310,"text":"and consuming sound consciously"},{"time":564343,"text":"and designing all our environments"},{"time":566070,"text":"consciously for sound?"},{"time":567547,"text":"That would be a world\nthat does sound beautiful,"},{"time":570671,"text":"and one where understanding\nwould be the norm,"},{"time":574582,"text":"and that is an idea worth spreading."}]},{"cues":[{"time":577255,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":578411,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}